data.meta_description: Paul Davis (16) Wide Receiver - 2023: Did not appear in any games for the Zips. PRIOR TO AKRON: A three-star recruit by 247Sports at Hart County High School....
data.text:
2023: Did not appear in any games for the Zips.

PRIOR TO AKRON: A three-star recruit by 247Sports at Hart County High School...a 2022 first-team all-region honoree and preseason all-state selection...2021 Georgia Elite Classical All-Star selection...a three-time all-state selection and four-time all-region honoree...registered 143 career catches for 2,027 receiving yards...tallied over 3,000 all-purpose yards en route to scoring 23 touchdowns...as a senior, tallied seven touchdowns, two interceptions and 504 receiving yards...selected to play in the 2021 Georgia vs. Florida game.

PERSONAL: Majoring in psychology...son of William and Dannette Davis.
